name: tiny skull studs
description: extra small skull studs. they're only 1/4" from the tip of the teeth to the top of the skull. great for everyday wear. cast in sterling silver, hand finished, oxidized to bring out the tiny details, and then polished to a bright shine. comes with sturdy silver butterfly backs.
